query:
SELECT COUNT(*)::bigint AS "total!"
    FROM links l
    WHERE
      ($1::timestamptz IS NULL AND $2::timestamptz IS NULL)
      OR EXISTS (
        SELECT 1
        FROM link_clicks lc
        WHERE lc.link_id = l.id
          AND ($1::timestamptz IS NULL OR lc.clicked_at >= $1)
          AND ($2::timestamptz IS NULL OR lc.clicked_at <  $2)
      )
